      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************

      ** +--- Start of Main processing -------------------------------+
      ** ¦                                                            ¦
      ** ¦ *INZSR is executed at program activation.                  ¦
      ** ¦                                                            ¦
      ** +------------------------------------------------------------+

      *****************************************************************
      * MAIN PROCEDURE                                                *
      *****************************************************************

      ** Initialise work variables

     C                   EVAL      IDx = 0
     C                   EVAL      WCurrency = *Blank
     C                   EVAL      WSpotRate = 0
     C                   EVAL      WDecPlace = 0
     C                   EVAL      WMulDivIn = *Blank
     C                   EVAL      WScaleExp = 0
     C                   EVAL      WIntCalcB = *Blank

     C                   EXSR      SRValCURR

      ** If an error has been found, set return code appropriately.
      ** Otherwise, update valid file fields.

     C                   IF        OKCCY <> 'Y'

     C                   EVAL      RetCodeIn = 'ERROR'

     C                   ELSE

     C                   EVAL      N1CCY = WCurrency
     C                   EVAL      N1CYDP = WDecPlace

     C                   EVAL      N2CCY = WCurrency
     C                   EVAL      N2CYDP = WDecPlace

     C                   ENDIF

      *                  ======
     C                   RETURN
      *                  ======

      *****************************************************************
      *  P R O G R A M   E N D                                        *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRValCURR - Validate Currency Code                           *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************

     C     SRValCURR     BEGSR

      ** Field is mandatory

     C                   IF        DDCCY = *Blanks

     C                   EVAL      OKCCY = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      IDx = IDx + 1
     C                   EVAL      FldNamXAr(IDx)= '#1CCY'
     C                   EVAL      MsgIdXAr(IDx) = 'MMM0142'
     C                   GOTO      EndValCurr

     C                   ENDIF

      ** Question Mark is valid only on repair and I/C screen inputs

     C     '?'           SCAN      DDCCY                                  05

     C                   IF        StrFoundIn = True

     C                   EVAL      PReDsp = 'Y'

     C                   IF        PMode = '*FRONT'

     C                   EVAL      OKCCY = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      IDx = IDx + 1
     C                   EVAL      FldNamXAr(IDx)= '#1CCY'
     C                   EVAL      MsgIdXAr(IDx) = 'MMM0202'
     C                   GOTO      EndValCurr

     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDIF

     ** Validate if Currency is existing

     C                   CALLB     'AOCURRR0'
     C                   PARM      *Blanks       PRtcd
     C                   PARM      '*KEY'        POptn
     C                   PARM      DDCCY         PKey
     C     SDCURR        PARM      SDCURR        DSSDY

     C                   IF        PRtcd <> *Blanks

     C                   IF        PRtcd = '*NOSEL '

     C                   EVAL      DDCCY  = *Blank
     C                   EVAL      OKCCY = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      IDx = IDx + 1
     C                   EVAL      FldNamXAr(IDx)= '#1CCY'
     C                   EVAL      MsgIdXAr(IDx) = 'MMM0142'
     C                   GOTO      EndValCurr

     C                   ELSE

     C                   EVAL      OKCCY = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      IDx = IDx + 1
     C                   EVAL      FldNamXAr(IDx)= '#1CCY'
     C                   EVAL      MsgIdXAr(IDx) = 'MMM0202'
     C                   GOTO      EndValCurr

     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ELSE

     C                   EVAL      WCurrency = A6CYCD
     C                   EVAL      DDCCY = A6CYCD
     C                   Z-ADD     A6SPRT        WSpotRate
     C                   Z-ADD     A6NBDP        WDecPlace
     C                   EVAL      WMulDivIn = A6MDIN
     C                   EVAL      WScaleExp = A6SCEX
     C                   EVAL      WIntCalCB = A6DICB

     C                   ENDIF

     C     EndValCurr    ENDSR

      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      * *INZSR - Program Initialisation routine                       *
      *                                                               *
      * Called by: Implicitly on program activation                   *
      *                                                               *
      * Calls: None                                                   *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************

     C     *INZSR        BEGSR

     C     *ENTRY        PLIST

      ** INPUT
      ** =====

      ** Return Code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn

      ** Mode = '*FRONT' (Front Office Transaction Interface)
      ** Mode = '      ' (Not Front Office Transaction Interface)
      ** Mode = '*RPR  ' (Repair function)
      ** Mode = '*SIN  ' (Screen input function)
     C                   PARM                    PMode

      ** New Deal in Screen Format
     C                   PARM                    NwDlScnFmt

      ** OUTPUT
      ** ======

      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIdXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr

      ** Internal funding deals error indicator file
     C                   PARM                    OkFlags

      ** New Deal in File Format of main deal
     C                   PARM                    NwDlFilFmt1

      ** New Deal in File Format of associated deal
     C                   PARM                    NwDlFilFmt2

      ** Redisplay screen flag
     C                   PARM                    PReDsp

      ** Deal Currency Details
     C                   PARM                    WSpotRate
     C                   PARM                    WDecPlace
     C                   PARM                    WMulDivIn
     C                   PARM                    WScaleExp
     C                   PARM                    WIntCalcB

      ** Program, module and procedure names for dbase error processing
      ** ==============================================================
      ** The following /COPY sets these values.

      /COPY ZACPYSRC,DBFIELDS

     C                   ENDSR

